=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> PrincipalList => ArrayRef[L<Paws::Kendra::Principal>]

A list of principal
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/kendra/latest/dg/API_Principal.html) lists
that define the hierarchy for which documents users should have access
to. Each hierarchical list specifies which user or group has allow or
deny access for each document.



